sub_title: Environmental and Social Officer  at FMO - Dutch entrepreneurial development bank
summary: I am an expert in environmental and social risk management for sustainable development projects particularly in the area of renewable energy. I possess very strong analytical and communication skills. I am passionate about sustainable development and want to contribute to reduce inequalities while ensuring a more sustainable use of natural resources of the planet. I am a strong defender of human rights and social justice. I have very good negotiation skills based on my Diplomatic experience and an open mind. I am a solution-oriented person with the ability to delivering successful investment projects. I am fluent in English, Spanish and Dutch.
